OL,3,CRetired workers left thousands out of
OL,4,Cpocket as pensions diminish
OL,6,FRetired workers say they've been left
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds out of pocket
OL,8,Fbecause their pensions, controlled by
OL,9,FHewlett Packard Enterprise, haven't
OL,10,Frisen in line with the cost of living.
OL,12,FThe company, based in Winnersh, is not
OL,13,Flegally obliged to index link pensions
OL,14,Fearned before 1997.
OL,16,FBut campaigners argue there's a moral
OL,17,Fduty and they're now taking their case
OL,18,Fto Parliament as they say the
OL,19,Fshortfall is impacting their quality
OL,20,Fof life.
