OL,3,CRetired workers left thousands out of
OL,4,Cpocket as pensions diminish
OL,6,FFormer employees Jane Foley and John
OL,7,FBarrett were both looking forward to
OL,8,Fcomfortable retirements but when the
OL,9,Ftime came they discovered their
OL,10,FHewlett Packard Enterprise pensions
OL,11,Fhadn't increased in line with
OL,12,Finflation - and so now face an
OL,13,Funcertain future.
OL,15,FJane said, "The impact on me is that
OL,16,Fmy pension is half of what I expected
OL,17,Fit to be. Literally the money that I
OL,18,Fhave from my state and my digital
OL,19,Fpension, I can just about meet my
OL,20,Fbills.
