OL,6,F"But as the years go on, my pension is
OL,7,Fgoing to be worth less and less. My
OL,8,Fbuying power is just going to be
OL,9,Fdiminished and I won't be able to meet
OL,10,Fthose bills and I don't know what's
OL,11,Fgoing to happen then."
OL,13,FJohn said, "Like Jane, I was not aware
OL,14,Fof the limitations that would be on
OL,15,Fpre '97 service, so it was a big
OL,16,Fsurprise when I discovered that the
OL,17,Fpension that I received in the late
OL,18,F90s is the same as the pension I
OL,19,Freceive today. So in 20 years, without
OL,20,Fan increase."
