OL,3,CRetired workers left thousands out of
OL,4,Cpocket as pensions diminish
OL,6,FAnd they are not alone. Two years ago
OL,7,Fa demonstration was held outside the
OL,8,FHewlett Packard offices in Winnersh.
OL,10,FThe pensioners who attended originally
OL,11,Fworked for Digital Equipment Company.
OL,12,FThat was bought out by another
OL,13,Forganisation that later merged with
OL,14,FHewlett Packard and since 2002 Hewlett
OL,15,FPackard Enterprise has been
OL,16,Fresponsible for the pensions.
OL,18,FCurrently there's no legal obligation
OL,19,Fto protect pensions against inflation
OL,20,Fbefore 1997, but campaigners say
OL,21,Fthat's just not fair.
