OL,6,FThey took their case to Parliament and
OL,7,FWokingham MP Clive Jones had this
OL,8,Fmessage for the company.J"These people
OL,9,Fhave given years and years of service
OL,10,Fto your company.
OL,12,F"They have helped you grow to be a
OL,13,Fworldwide company and to make
OL,14,Fsignificant profits for the, the
OL,15,Fdirectors or senior managers of the
OL,16,Fcompany to have decent bonuses and for
OL,17,Fshareholders to have decent dividends.
