OL,6,F"The decision on whether to grant
OL,7,Fdiscretionary increases to relevant
OL,8,Fpensioners is given careful
OL,9,Fconsideration and is made based on a
OL,10,Fnumber of different factors. It is
OL,11,Freviewed on an annual basis."
OL,13,FHPE said the next review is due
OL,14,Ftowards the end of this year and
OL,15,Fbeginning of 2026 and the announcement
OL,16,Fwould be made in the spring.
